campaigns.name: Mandatory for Company Registration via Online System at MLVT
campaigns.subject: HRINC Marketing
campaigns.html:
Dear Beloved Clients

Greeting from HRINC Compliance Team. 

I am pleased to inform you that Ministry of Labor and Vocational Training (MLVT) has launched the online system that is required for all existing companies and new company to re-register/register via online system at MLVT from 11 January 2021 onward. So please let us know if you need our services for this processing.

You can update your preferences or unsubscribe from this list.

campaigns.name: Clean-out your Closet Campaign!!
campaigns.subject: Clean-out Your Closet Campaign!!
campaigns.html:
Every year HRINC tries to support needy associations. This year we are working with the Children’s Restaurant (Les Restaurants Des Enfants – LRDE) again and for the first time with the Cambodia Cyclo Association. 

We will support the organizations with basic necessities which we often take for granted.  Besides clothes, food and schooling materials are also important given the devastating impact of COVID-19 on livelihoods.

You can update your preferences or unsubscribe from this list.
